<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Thu, 03 Feb 2022 00:50:15 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>黃大仙祠推網上祈福平台，定期由道長代向神靈上稟</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/03/wong-tai-sin-temple/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=wong-tai-sin-temple</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 03 Feb 2022 00:49:22 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[網上祈福]]></category><category><![CDATA[黃大仙祠]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084462</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>本港疫情反覆，各地相繼出現不同來源的確診個案。為保障大眾安全，黃大仙祠宣布推出網上參神服務，讓善信不受時間或地 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>本港疫情反覆，各地相繼出現不同來源的確診個案。為保障大眾安全，黃大仙祠宣布推出網上參神服務，讓善信不受時間或地理影響向黃大仙祠祈願。該園道長將會為在網上祈福平台祈福的善信，定期就有關內容代為祈福，並於宗教儀式中誦經及禱告，向神靈上稟，整個過程莊嚴肅穆。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05-694x389.png" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05-694x389.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05-1280x718.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05-1536x861.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.18.05.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>善信只需輸入姓名、性別、出生日期、電郵地址及居住地點的個人資料後，便可寫下不多於 15 字的祈福內容，而平台亦有提供健康、家庭、財運及姻緣等多個祈福主題讓善信選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.19.03.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.19.03-442x580.png" alt="" width="442" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.19.03-442x580.png 442w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.19.03-686x900.png 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.19.03-768x1008.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-上午 3.19.03.png 1082w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 442px" /></a></p><p>確認資料後便會自動寄出祈福內容，道長將於日後禮懺科儀中向仙師上稟善信的祈願。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="http://www.wongtaisintemple.org.hk/online-praying">黃大仙祠網上參神網頁</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
