</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>FB、IG 虛擬頭像新版本，可錄動畫、變表情貼圖、插入 IG Story</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/03/3d-avatars/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=3d-avatars</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 03 Feb 2022 00:37:19 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Facebook]]></category><category><![CDATA[instagram]]></category><category><![CDATA[Messenger]]></category><category><![CDATA[Meta]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084377</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Meta 宣布，Instagram Stories 加入 3D 虛擬頭像，並為 Facebook、Messen [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Meta 宣布，Instagram Stories 加入 3D 虛擬頭像，並為 Facebook、Messenger 更新其虛擬頭像。為了加強 3D 虛擬頭像與用戶的相似性，Meta 表示會為頭像設定加入更多的編輯選擇，例如不同面貌、助聽器、及輪椅等，令頭像更細緻和真實。虛擬頭像除可用作帳戶的頭像外，更可錄製動畫、變成類似 Apple「Memoji」的表情貼圖，也可插入 IG Story 之中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16-467x580.jpg" alt="" width="467" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16-467x580.jpg 467w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16-725x900.jpg 725w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16-768x953.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16-1238x1536.jpg 1238w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.16.jpg 1289w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 467px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08-721x900.jpg 721w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08-768x959.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08-1230x1536.jpg 1230w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.08.jpg 1281w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26-460x580.jpg" alt="" width="460" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26-460x580.jpg 460w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26-714x900.jpg 714w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26-768x968.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26-1218x1536.jpg 1218w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.26.jpg 1269w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 460px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12-451x580.jpg" alt="" width="451" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12-451x580.jpg 451w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12-699x900.jpg 699w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12-768x989.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12-1193x1536.jpg 1193w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-03-上午 8.30.12.jpg 1243w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 451px" /></a></p><p>用戶可以為不同平台的角色創建不同頭像。Meta 稱希望能增強頭像的表達能力，令頭像更栩栩如生。此外更致力將用戶的頭像更容易轉移到不同地方，以發展更多的可能性。由於有關功能仍處於試用階段，因此暫只有美國、加拿大及墨西哥的用戶可優先試用。</p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/1/31/22910271/meta-3d-avatars-instagram-stories-messenger-facebook">The Verge</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 :<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"> <u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
