</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Gucci AirPods Max 保護套，賣$7700 特徵逐格睇</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/03/gucci-airpods-max/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=gucci-airpods-max</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 03 Feb 2022 00:13:33 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084480</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 推出 AirPods 耳機系列的 AirPods Max 在美國售價 549 美元（約 4200 元港 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 推出 AirPods 耳機系列的 AirPods Max 在美國售價 549 美元（約 4200 元港幣），使用者都會購買耳機套以更好保護耳機。奢侈品牌 Gucci 看中耳機的價值，為其設計製作 Ophidia case 耳機套，要價 980 美元（約 7700 元港幣），比耳機的價格還高。</p><p>據官方網站顯示，Gucci Ophidia case 耳機套是網路銷售的獨家產品，利用經典元素結合復古和現代設計，以環保材質製作而成，棕色皮革上印著 Gucci 的雙 G logo，還有可調式肩帶，內側印著意思是屬於今天的 Hodiernum 字樣。與許多 AirPods Max 配件一樣，Gucci 的保護套也露出 AirPods Max 的頭蓋部分，以便於攜帶。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.32.05.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.32.05-694x384.png" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.32.05-694x384.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.32.05-768x425.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.32.05.png 1008w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.29.46.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.29.46-694x433.png" alt="" width="694" height="433" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.29.46-694x433.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.29.46-768x479.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.29.46.png 1264w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.30.07.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084486" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.30.07-601x580.png" alt="" width="601" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.30.07-601x580.png 601w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.30.07-933x900.png 933w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.30.07-768x741.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-02-12.30.07.png 1010w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 601px" /></a></p><p>Gucci 除為 AirPods Max 設計保護套之外，亦為一般的標準耳機設計專用保護套，售價 920 美元（約 7100 元港幣），比 AirPods Max 專用版本低。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.iclarified.com/84501/gucci-launches-980-case-for-apple-airpods-max">iclarified</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
